1
00:00:10,877 --> 00:00:12,012
It's so organized.

2
00:00:12,746 --> 00:00:14,481
If he saw my suitcase,

3
00:00:15,348 --> 00:00:16,416
he'd totally laugh at me.

4
00:00:34,667 --> 00:00:35,802
Why are you crouching here?

5
00:00:36,803 --> 00:00:38,170
I was waiting for you.

6
00:00:38,171 --> 00:00:39,873
I was worried you'd passed out in there.

7
00:00:49,182 --> 00:00:50,450
Come on, get up.

8
00:00:52,051 --> 00:00:53,085
My legs are asleep.

9
00:00:53,086 --> 00:00:54,086
Asleep?

10
00:00:55,255 --> 00:00:56,156
You okay?

11
00:00:56,156 --> 00:00:57,156
Yeah.

12
00:01:04,497 --> 00:01:06,166
I'm good, thanks.

13
00:01:08,501 --> 00:01:09,736
Why don't you get some sleep?

14
00:01:17,877 --> 00:01:19,112
Go lie down in the room.

15
00:01:20,313 --> 00:01:20,914
No, I'll just stay here.

16
00:01:20,915 --> 00:01:22,449
Just for a little bit.

17
00:01:30,056 --> 00:01:32,225
I have some cold medicine. Hang on.

18
00:01:33,860 --> 00:01:35,161
I hate taking medicine.

19
00:01:37,130 --> 00:01:38,865
Is it because of the accident?

20
00:01:42,335 --> 00:01:43,770
You're finally noticing me.

21
00:01:44,871 --> 00:01:46,038
To get ready for this trip,

22
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:47,807
I've only been sleeping two hours a night.

23
00:01:48,241 --> 00:01:50,076
I'm fine. I just need to lie down.

24
00:01:57,851 --> 00:01:59,552
If my cousin saw this,

25
00:02:00,653 --> 00:02:02,522
he'd definitely call me pathetic.
